results.original_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
results.title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
results.overview: Anakin Skywalker, a young slave strong with the Force, is discovered on Tatooine. Meanwhile, the evil Sith have returned, enacting their plot for revenge against the Jedi.

results.title: The Beginning : Making 'Episode I'
results.overview: The entire process of making Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace (1999) is shown here in this documentary. From pre-production through post-production we get to see visual effects meetings, John Williams music sessions and even the storm that wiped out the pod-racers & props
